# Proposed Hardened Architecture

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "Branch Offices (9 cities)"
        B1[Branch Router]
        B2[Branch Users<br/>MFA Required]
    end
    
    subgraph "Data Center - Perimeter Layer"
        FW1[Next-Gen Firewall<br/>Egress Filtering + DNS Filtering]
        IPS[IPS/IDS Sensors]
    end
    
    subgraph "Data Center - Segmented Network"
        subgraph "DMZ - Public Facing"
            WEB[Web Server<br/>Customer Portal<br/>WAF Enabled]
        end
        
        subgraph "Application Tier"
            APP[App Server<br/>Internal Tools<br/>No Direct Internet]
        end
        
        subgraph "Data Tier"
            DB[(Database<br/>Encrypted at Rest<br/>No Internet Access)]
        end
        
        subgraph "Management Jump Host"
            JUMP[Secure Jump Host<br/>Session Recording]
        end
    end
    
    subgraph "Observability Layer"
        SIEM[SIEM + NSM<br/>NetFlow + App Logs]
    end
    
    INTERNET((Internet))
    
    B1 --> FW1
    B2 --> WEB
    FW1 --> WEB
    WEB --> APP
    APP --> DB
    WEB -.-> JUMP
    APP -.-> JUMP
    WEB --> SIEM
    APP --> SIEM
    DB --> SIEM
    
